genresAdvancedInfo.name: bohol indie
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Bohol Indie is a music genre originating from the province of Bohol in the Philippines. It is characterized by its indie rock sound with a touch of traditional Filipino music. The lyrics often reflect the beauty of the province and its culture, making it relatable to the local audience. The genre has gained popularity in recent years, with many local artists making a name for themselves in the music scene.
